== Configuration Regimes

[[rbrr_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbrr_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Repository Regime

[[rbrd_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbrd_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Depot Regime

[[rbrp_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbrp_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Payor Regime

[[rbro_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbro_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle OAuth Regime

[[rbrv_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbrv_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Vessel Regime

[[rbra_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbra_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Authentication Regime

[[rbrn_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbrn_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Nameplate Regime

[[rbrs_prefix]]
//axl_voices axrg_prefix
{rbrs_prefix}::
Recipe Bottle Station Regime

=== Consumer Filesystem Layout

[[rbsld_moorings]]
//axl_voices axtu_path
{rbsld_moorings}::
The moorings directory — the single root for all {rbtr_consumer} configuration.
At its root sit the installation-wide regime assignment files; each {at_nameplate} adds a subdirectory named by its {rbrn_moniker}, and vessel definitions live under {rbrr_vessel_dir}.
Each regime's exact file location is stated in that regime's definition.

=== Repository Regime (RBRR)

The
regime
defines installation-wide configuration that rarely changes and is shared across all
{at_recipe_bottle}
operations.
This specification documents only the subset of RBRR variables relevant to
{gcp_service}
operations.

[[rbrr_regime]]
//axvr_regime axf_bash axrd_file_sourced axrd_singleton
{rbrr_regime}::
Repository-wide configuration and installation-wide settings shared across all
{at_recipe_bottle}
operations.
File-sourced singleton at {rbsld_moorings}rbrr.env.

[[rbrr_secrets_dir]]
//axl_voices axrg_variable axtu_path
{rbrr_secrets_dir}::
Directory containing service account credential files for all operational roles.
Validated to exist before credential file paths are derived.

[[rbrr_retriever_rbra_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_retriever_rbra_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_retriever}
{rbtgi_rbra_file}
for container image operations.
Derived from
{rbrr_secrets_dir}
as `retriever/rbra.env`.

[[rbrr_director_rbra_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_director_rbra_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_director}
{rbtgi_rbra_file}
for build submission and image management.
Derived from
{rbrr_secrets_dir}
as `director/rbra.env`.

[[rbrr_governor_rbra_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_governor_rbra_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_governor}
{rbtgi_rbra_file}
for
{gcp_project_id}
administration.
Derived from
{rbrr_secrets_dir}
as `governor/rbra.env`.

[[rbrr_payor_rbro_file]]
//axl_voices axrd_constructed axtu_path
{rbrr_payor_rbro_file}::
Path to the
{rbtr_payor}
{rbro_regime}
credentials file for OAuth operations.
Derived from
{rbrr_secrets_dir}

